    },
    {
      "_key": "1a09f8a253c4d9cb123ec279f81ad8fe",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "iFz7YKPzxbcQjtwtctQ2xA",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "まとめ"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "h2"
    },
    {
      "_key": "summary-514ed880-63ab-4856-ab54-2dcc7171e5db",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "summary-span-a2010239-c996-4354-b5cd-9b4131d408f6",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "「指示が怖い…」をなくす！看護助手のあなたへ、スムーズな指示受けのコツでお伝えした内容を振り返ると、日々の現場で大切にしたいポイントが幾つか見えてきます。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "summary-3e2f08cb-dfd6-430a-87e4-e6207381202f",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "summary-span-01207ed6-a068-4b14-87b2-bbb3892e9c21",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "すぐに試しやすい行動のヒントは次の通りです。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "summary-bullet-db8ed182-b626-4831-807d-8e9b8f6e14c7",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "summary-bullet-span-7a516d27-c637-41aa-a9c6-cf7a843f63ed",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "あわせて読みたい"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "summary-bullet-894cdc03-f776-45a3-8109-6d60144b5759",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "summary-bullet-span-bbe13d6a-a461-422f-9942-f85678cd98a1",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "指示を正確に聞き取るための3つのステップの視点でステップ1：まずは「聞く体制」を整えるに目を向ける"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "summary-bullet-b0edc59d-f74b-45a7-8d2f-451436c75222",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "summary-bullet-span-4faff6ac-9651-4b15-972b-21b45e9384e8",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "指示を正確に聞き取るための3つのステップの視点でステップ2：重要な情報は「復唱」するに目を向ける"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "summary-ab44ca39-6b6d-4e2e-979e-f736e96fd7cb",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "summary-span-ec4ae351-b06d-4a0c-bcdf-bfc6c0ca7d03",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "あわてず一歩ずつ、チームと情報を共有しながら進めれば大丈夫です。今日の学びを小さく実践し、次の勤務につなげていきましょう。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
